====== Usage ======

vid2mp4:

  $ vid2mp4.sh <source_file> <target_file>

vid2mp4_seek:
  
  $ vid2mp4_seek.h <source_file> <targe_file> <start_time>

vid2mp4_timed:

  $ vid2mp4_timed.sh <source_file> <target_file> <start_time> <duration>

  star_time, duration: is seconds, or in the "hh.mm.ss[.xxx]" syntax

vid2mp4_sized:

  $ vid2mp4_sized.sh <wxh> <source_file> <target_file>

batch_conversion.py:

  $ python batch_conversion.py <specs_file>

 
  
 
